1512
01:02:28,900 --> 01:02:30,580
 A ovoga,

1513
01:02:30,580 --> 01:02:32,460
 onda je bila ta zadnja godina

1514
01:02:32,460 --> 01:02:33,200
 specke

1515
01:02:33,200 --> 01:02:34,140
 i ispit

1516
01:02:34,140 --> 01:02:35,780
