1523
01:02:42,660 --> 01:02:44,020
 pružila se prilika,

1524
01:02:44,020 --> 01:02:45,200
 takva prilika se

1525
01:02:45,200 --> 01:02:46,260
 po meni

1526
01:02:46,260 --> 01:02:47,880
 ne odbija

1527
01:02:47,880 --> 01:02:48,820
 zato što ti je

1528
01:02:48,820 --> 01:02:49,920
 to iskustvo

1529
01:02:49,920 --> 01:02:51,760
 i jedno učenje

1530
01:02:51,760 --> 01:02:52,680
 za cijeli život

1531
01:02:52,680 --> 01:02:53,240
 vrijedno

1532
01:02:53,240 --> 01:02:54,540
 i znala sam

1533
01:02:54,540 --> 01:02:55,440
 da želim raditi

1534
01:02:55,440 --> 01:02:56,700
 tada u bolnici

1535
01:02:56,700 --> 01:02:58,080
 i željela sam

1536
01:02:58,080 --> 01:02:59,860
 dalje se educirati

1537
01:02:59,860 --> 01:03:01,020
 znači što sam radila

1538
01:03:01,020 --> 01:03:01,720
 recimo

1539
01:03:01,720 --> 01:03:02,460
 i čitala

1540
01:03:02,460 --> 01:03:03,600
 i tijekom trudnoća

1541
01:03:03,600 --> 01:03:04,440
 i kad su oni

1542
01:03:04,440 --> 01:03:06,220
 malo bili veći

1543
01:03:06,220 --> 01:03:07,020
 kad ti nije bilo

1544
01:03:07,020 --> 01:03:07,520
 ono dan

1545
01:03:07,520 --> 01:03:08,220
 da stvarno

1546
01:03:08,220 --> 01:03:09,680
 24 sata hraniš

1547
01:03:09,680 --> 01:03:10,280
 presplatiš

1548
01:03:10,280 --> 01:03:10,580
 pele

1549
01:03:10,580 --> 01:03:11,280
 ne pereš

1550
01:03:11,280 --> 01:03:11,820
 i tako

1551
01:03:11,820 --> 01:03:13,200
 tako da

1552
01:03:13,200 --> 01:03:14,540
 ako je neko

1553
01:03:14,540 --> 01:03:15,840
 na mom mjestu

1554
01:03:15,840 --> 01:03:17,100
 bilo koje struke

1555
01:03:17,100 --> 01:03:18,600
 ne treba odustajati

1556
01:03:18,600 --> 01:03:19,420
 to se sve

1557
01:03:19,420 --> 01:03:20,560
 može uskladiti

1558
01:03:20,560 --> 01:03:21,160
 naravno

1559
01:03:21,160 --> 01:03:22,100
 svakako

1560
01:03:22,100 --> 01:03:23,120
 uz suport

1561
01:03:23,120 --> 01:03:24,820
 cijele obitelji

1562
01:03:24,820 --> 01:03:26,280
 da

1563
01:03:26,280 --> 01:03:28,520
 svako ima drugačiju priču

1564
01:03:28,520 --> 01:03:28,900
 ali

1565
01:03:28,900 --> 01:03:30,140
 evo

1566
01:03:30,140 --> 01:03:31,220
 držim fige

1567
01:03:31,220 --> 01:03:31,980
 ako je netko

1568
01:03:31,980 --> 01:03:33,200
 tko upravo sluša

1569
01:03:33,200 --> 01:03:34,420
 na toj prekretnici

1570
01:03:34,420 --> 01:03:35,680
 da ne odustaje

1571
01:03:35,680 --> 01:03:35,920
 od

1572
01:03:35,920 --> 01:03:37,480
 od svojih

1573
01:03:37,480 --> 01:03:38,300
 snova

1574
01:03:38,300 --> 01:03:38,960
 i želja

1575
01:03:38,960 --> 01:03:40,240
 a spomenuli ste

1576
01:03:40,240 --> 01:03:40,740
 da vam je od uvijek

1577
01:03:40,740 --> 01:03:41,360
 bila želja

1578
01:03:41,360 --> 01:03:42,620
 baviti se ovim

1579
01:03:42,620 --> 01:03:43,600
 raditi s djecom

1580
01:03:43,600 --> 01:03:44,420
 zašto?

1581
01:03:44,420 --> 01:03:46,260
 pa nekako

1582
01:03:46,260 --> 01:03:46,320
 ovoga

1583
01:03:46,320 --> 01:03:48,120
 znala sam

1584
01:03:48,120 --> 01:03:49,420
 dok sam još bila mala

1585
01:03:49,420 --> 01:03:49,860
 da želim

1586
01:03:49,860 --> 01:03:50,800
 ja sam govorila od uvijek

1587
01:03:50,800 --> 01:03:52,140
 da želim biti doktorica

1588
01:03:52,140 --> 01:03:52,820
 znači uopće

1589
01:03:52,820 --> 01:03:53,880
 ništa drugo

1590
01:03:53,880 --> 01:03:54,640
 nije dolazilo

1591
01:03:54,640 --> 01:03:55,480
 jeste iz lječnička

1592
01:03:55,480 --> 01:03:56,180
 obitelji ili?

1593
